<para0><title>PURPOSE AND SCOPE</title>
<para>This manual may pertain to some or all types and series of a
model of aircraft and may, This manual contains complete requirements
for therefore, contain requirements applicable to specific accomplishing
scheduled maintenance on this aircraft equipment that is not installed
on an individual during its entire service life. It establishes inspection,
aircraft. When this situation is encountered, those accessory replacement,
and functional check flight requirements that are not applicable should
be requirements for the aircraft and airborne equipment. disregarded.</para>
<note>
<para>This manual has been developed solely as a demonstration document
for this document type within Arbortext software. None of the content
is factual. </para>
</note>
<subpara1><title>Limitations</title><para>This manual does not contain
symbol preceding the requirements. Requirements detailed instructions
for troubleshooting to find causes in this manual are not in sequence;
applicable work for malfunctioning, nor does it contain instructions
for cards will specify the sequence. repair, adjustment, or other
means of rectifying defective conditions.</para>
</subpara1>
<subpara1><title>Applicability</title><para>This manual may pertain
to some  or all types and series of a model of aircraft and may, This
manual contains complete requirements for therefore, contain requirements
applicable to specific accomplishing scheduled maintenance on this
aircraft equipment that is not installed on an individual during its
entire service life. It establishes inspection, aircraft. When this
situation is encountered, those accessory replacement, and functional
check flight requirements that are not applicable should be requirements
for the aircraft and airborne equipment. disregarded. </para>
</subpara1>
