</front><body numcols="1"><schedreq>
<title>Scheduled Inspection and Maintenance Requirements</title>
<preflt>
<title>PREFLIGHT</title>
<sectnote><title>Preflight/Preoperation</title>
<para>Items that, due to environment, are subject to damage by outside
forces, such as ground equipment, maintenance crews, elements of nature,
etc. </para>
<para>Items that, due to design characteristics, normally require
service or verification of service prior to the first flight/operation
of the day. </para>
</sectnote>
<actiontbl>
<actionblk>
<action id="srwc1" label="x" cardno="cardno att" wucsys="73"
wucsub="XXX" area="area att" minute="minute att"><?Pub Dtl><task><para>XXXThis
is the FIRST Scheduled Requirement included here. This is the <emphasis
type="b">PRIMARY</emphasis> action element</para></task>
<subaction1 cardno="cardno" wucsys="23" wucsub="zzz" area="AFT"
minute="minute"><task><para>This is a secondary or <emphasis type="b">SUBACTION
#1</emphasis> for PreFlight</para></task>
