minute="minute"><task><para>This is <emphasis type="b">SUBACTION 2</emphasis>.
There can be one or more subaction 2s.</para></task></subaction2>
<subaction2 cardno="cardno att" wucsys="73" wucsub="XXX" area="area att"
minute="minute att"><task><para>This is a para within a task. This
