<endrunway>
<title>end of runway</title>
<sectnote><title>End of Runway</title>
<para>Items that are subject to damage during ground operations or
are not readily apparent until after operation begins. </para>
<para>Items, such as panels and doors, that must be secure prior to
flight/operation</para>
<para>Items, such as down locks, safety pins, and protective covers,
that must be removed prior to flight/operation. </para>
</sectnote>
<actiontbl>
<actionblk>
<action cardno="cardno att" wucsys="73" wucsub="XXX" area="area att"
