<bpostflt><title>basic postflight</title>
<sectnote><title>Basic Postflight/Postoperation</title>
<para>Items that due to their operational characteristics are subject
to loss of lubricant, fluids, air, etc., during flight/operation. </para>
<para>Items that due to flight/operation are subject to damage such
as impact, foreign objects, etc., during operation. </para>
<para>Items of critical nature that are subject to developing defects
which are not readily apparent to the users during operation. </para>
<para>Items, such as down locks, safety pins, and protective covers,
that must be installed prior to maintenance. </para>
</sectnote>
