<hpostflt><?Pub Dtl>
<title>hourly postflight</title>
<sectnote><title>Hourly postflight/postoperation</title>
<para>Items that due to their installation characteristics are subject
to excessive chafing and insecure mounting. </para>
<para>Items that are subject to extreme heat conditions. </para>
<para>Items that due to their design characteristics are subject to
developing leaks or unusual cracks. </para>
<para>Items that require more frequent verification of serviceability
or operation than the periodic/phased/isochronal inspection interval. </para>
<para>Items that require more frequent verification of service than
the periodic/phased/isochronal inspection interval. </para>
</sectnote>
