<specoccur><title>Special occurrences</title>
<sectnote><para>Items that due to their physical characteristics are
subject to deterioration after long periods of service. </para>
<para>Items that due to their structural characteristics are subject
to fatigue after long periods of service.</para>
<para>Items that due to their function within a system are subject
to damage from specific events, such as hard landings, violent maneuvers,
hot starts, false starts, etc. </para>
