unit code, noun, FSC and part number for which base level (organizational
and intermediate) repair restrictions are established. A description
of repair restrictions shall be provided. Items listed shall be limited
to recoverable type items. Items which are Source, Maintenance and
Recoverability (SMR) coded &ldquo;depot repair only&rdquo; shall not
be listed.FLIGHT DECK WINDOWS FOR CRACKS, DELAMINATION, SEALANT FOR
DETERIORATION.WINDSHIELD HEAT CONNECTIONS FOR SECURITY, WINDSHIELD
HEAT WIRING FOR CUTS,CRACKS, DETERIORATION, AND BARE WIRES</para>
